{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Witch's Cauldron</strong> \u2013 a medieval witch simulator from the young indie team <strong>Harvey Games.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You\u2019ll practice your craft in a town where good rumors spread just as fast as bad ones, with the latter quickly reaching the ears of inquisitors. Balancing your popularity among townsfolk and the inquisitors\u2019 growing attention is essential for survival here. And if your witch\u2019s intuition tells you the end is near, you can always find refuge in another town\u2014there are plenty nearby.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251010/extras/SkinWishlist.gif?t=1730107054\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But that\u2019s for the future. For now, bards, vampires, innkeepers, and even the king himself come to pay their respects! Fulfill their requests, brew potions, but remember: every good or evil deed will bring inevitable consequences.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251010/extras/what_en.png?t=1730107054\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 60 unique characters, each with their own story and multiple playthrough options;</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A vast array of potions, each capable of leading to a unique story outcome;</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A variety of witch skins that unlock unique quests, present challenges, and subtly alter gameplay;<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251010/extras/G3Skin.gif?t=1730107054\" /></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">6 main story endings that affect not only your life but also the entire kingdom;<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251010/extras/G2.gif?t=1730107054\" /></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Numerous nighttime events reflecting the outcomes of your choices;</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">High replayability, allowing you to explore the world, uncover the witch\u2019s past, and understand the kingdom\u2019s morals.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251010/extras/Card.gif?t=1730107054\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251010/extras/lifWitch_en.png?t=1730107054\" />Each day, locals will visit you. Some come seeking healing, others out of curiosity, and some with a desire to engage in darker deeds. Their fates are in your hands\u2014it\u2019s up to you to decide how to handle them.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251010/extras/demon.gif?t=1730107054\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251010/extras/lifcaul_en.png?t=1730107054\" />With your choice of potions, you influence the course of events. However, only a few basic potions are available from the start; you\u2019ll need to unlock new and more complex ones by mixing ingredients or obtaining recipes and hints from NPCs.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251010/extras/game.gif?t=1730107054\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251010/extras/lul_en.png?t=1730107054\" />Unlocked potions, no matter how each story ends, will carry over to your next life cycle. The abundance of potions and story twists allows for a highly variable playthrough experience. Some endings, potions, and game mechanics will only be available after completing the main story once or reaching certain game events that conclude the story.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251010/extras/cats_step.gif?t=1730107054\" /></p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Friends in high places","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2251010/9446572b453dd43d5155f9833d6e2fe5100a15bc.jpg"},{"name":"The pyre","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2251010/387e131a0c5327cebfa77c42377ad47f6f29d765.jpg"},{"name":"Torches and pitchforks","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2251010/c658e9ceb3badc8b928ef6c56148581275949fa3.jpg"},{"name":"The fraud","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2251010/14b3f6fa11ae156f93ca5f3a33b037c9130489fc.jpg"},{"name":"Robbery victim","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2251010/71484c9a6f3b6e5add16defac377f257f6d15799.jpg"},{"name":"The circle","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2251010/915b6c5928b9061b0a2170b7c3eb654a9ab13376.jpg"},{"name":"Power play","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2251010/ed9fd0b66f02e3eeb06f944db7fa2003353a9368.jpg"},{"name":"Revolt","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2251010/47f366d90577d4cb5e94ff7bd8a7e98a2fde561b.jpg"},{"name":"White hat","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2251010/16a575bd26244d81496a416c500f95016f4f7ec2.jpg"},{"name":"Sackcloth","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2251010/c89aeb3cc9b409480b2fab07361f5b4c16bcce6f.jpg"}],"total":66},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251010/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730107054","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamsta